<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

<h3>What makes these the world's hottest corn chips?</h3>
<p>These chips are infused with a super-hot puree containing three of the world's hottest chilli peppers: Carolina Reaper, Scorpion, and Bhut Jolokia, then topped with additional Carolina Reaper powder for maximum heat. This combination of multiple extreme chilli varieties makes them genuinely among the hottest corn chips available.</p>

<h3>Are these chips safe to eat if I have a sensitive stomach?</h3>
<p>No, these chips are not recommended for people with pre-existing gastrointestinal issues, heartburn, or acid reflux. We strongly advise consulting with a healthcare professional before attempting to eat extremely spicy foods like these chips.</p>


