<h3>How much should I eat when trying these chips for the first time?</h3>
<p>Start with just one chip to test your tolerance before eating a handful. The heat intensity is extreme, so it's better to gauge your reaction with a small amount first rather than risk overwhelming your palate and digestive system.</p>

<h3>Can I finish a whole packet of these chips in one sitting?</h3>
<p>The challenge to finish the whole packet in one go is more of a dare for extreme spice enthusiasts—most people will find even a few chips more than enough. We recommend spacing your consumption and definitely not attempting the whole packet unless you have serious experience with extreme heat. If you're planning a party or event and want to include these as a daring snack challenge, you might want to explore <a href="https://sweetsworld.com.au/candy-guides/party-bags/">party snack ideas</a> to balance them with other options for your guests.</p>

<h3>Where do these world's hottest corn chips come from?</h3>
